<h3 width=100% style='background: grey; padding: 3px; color: white;'>Events</h3>
Information sharing for BAMRU Events (meetings, trainings, operations).

Meetings and trainings can be scheduled, and calendar data is
exported to our public website and Google calendars.

Operations can be tracked, and the DO can record member checkin/checkout times.
SMSO reports and summary statics are generated.

<b><%= link_to events_url, '/events'  %></b>
